            glPopMatrix
        Case K_P_BATTLE_MODEL:
            ComputePModelBoundingBox P_Model, p_min, p_max
            SetCameraAroundModel p_min, p_max, PanX, PanY, PanZ + DIST, _
                alpha, Beta, Gamma, 1, 1, 1

